1 the GEANT4 setup
To setup the environment, execute the following commands:

. /afs/cern.ch/sw/lcg/external/gcc/4.3.2/x86_64-slc5/setup.sh
cd /afs/cern.ch/sw/lcg/app/releases/ROOT/5.30.00/x86_64-slc5-gcc43-opt/root;. ./bin/thisroot.sh; cd -
export G4WORKDIR= (director of your G4 installation)/Geant4/9.5.p01/x86_64-slc5-gcc43
source /afs/cern.ch/sw/lcg/external/geant4/9.5.p01/x86_64-slc5-gcc43/setup.sh

To run, cd to the test directory, and do :

$G4WORKDIR/bin/$G4SYSTEM/DmpSimu macro_proton.mac

2 the SCONS SETUP
you can use either Makefile or Scons to build the executable.
